insert into proizvod (proizvodID, cena, sifra, naziv, active) values (#[payload.proizvodID], #[payload.cena], #[payload.sifra], #[payload.naziv], #[payload.active]) on duplicate key update cena=values(cena), sifra=values(sifra), naziv=values(naziv), active=values(active);
